<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>扇子的风整整刮了一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空也被风刮到了很远的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他落地的时候，已经离铁扇公主的山很远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到附近有座山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那座山看上去很眼熟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“须弥山！”悟空说，“灵吉菩萨住在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许他可以帮我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他曾经打败过黄风怪的吹风术。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空去了灵吉菩萨那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灵吉菩萨正坐在他的花园里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，灵吉菩萨。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，悟空。”灵吉菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很高兴又见面了。我正想喝杯茶呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和灵吉菩萨一起喝茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把铁扇公主的事情告诉了灵吉菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灵吉菩萨给了悟空一个小石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把它放在你的口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有了它，你就不会被大风吹走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢，灵吉菩萨。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想留下来吃午饭吗？”灵吉菩萨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不了，谢谢。”悟空说，“我得回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我得从铁扇公主那里拿到扇子，才能继续去西天取经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回到了铁扇公主的洞门前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开门！”他大叫，“我需要你的扇子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她皱了皱鼻子说：“你怎么又来了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她举起了扇子。“这次我要更用力地扇。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主生气地扇着扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵强风刮过了。悟空没有动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主更生气了。“你怎么会......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“灵吉菩萨给了我一颗定风珠。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的扇子现在没法把我扇走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抽出了金箍棒。“现在把扇子给我吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主飞快地逃回了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还没来得及关上门，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空就变成了一只蟋蟀，迅速地跳进了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地跟在铁扇公主后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主走进房间坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把扇子放进了自己的袍子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空这猴子太可恶了！”她自言自语道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他强迫我可怜的孩子向善。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他又想借我的宝贝扇子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主端起一杯水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在她要喝水的时候，悟空跳进了杯子里。咕咚！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在铁扇公主的胃里，悟空变回了原形。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘣！砰！嘣！砰！悟空拳打脚踢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主痛得捂着肚子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！那水里有什么？我的肚子好痛啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我！”悟空大叫，“我在你的肚子里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把那扇子给我，不然我就一直打你！”嘣！砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请住手！”铁扇公主大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把扇子给你。你快点儿出来吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空从铁扇公主的鼻子里跳了出来，变回了原形。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我扇子！”他说。铁扇公主站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从袍子里拿出了扇子。“给你，拿走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回到了村子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉了大家他是怎么骗铁扇公主的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”唐僧说，“现在我们可以继续上路了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们谢过了老人，继续西行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们来到了一个山坡上，看到了火焰山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火焰覆盖了周围所有的土地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”悟空说。悟空用力扇着扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼！一阵强风刮向火焰山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“很快我们就可以......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>忽然，火焰山上响起了轰鸣声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那火越来越旺，布满了整个天空！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>